# Cloudflare Pages Routing

# Redirect old properties subdomain to new realestate subdomain
https://properties.erposus.com/*  https://realestate.erposus.com/:splat  301
http://properties.erposus.com/*  https://realestate.erposus.com/:splat  301

# Redirect only root domain to realestate subdomain
# This allows erposus.com/web and other paths to work normally
https://erposus.com  https://realestate.erposus.com  301
http://erposus.com  https://realestate.erposus.com  301

# SPA fallback (only for this site's pages)
/*  /index.html  200
